{"type":"message","id":"c51240c8","parentId":"70dfb94e","timestamp":"2026-05-21T03:48:25.232Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is providing a password: d8DUQdqH\n\nLet me try to fetch the Apifox document again with this password, or more likely, the user wants me to use this password to access the protected document.\n\nActually, Apifox docs typically require authentication. The password might be for accessing the doc. But web_fetch doesn't support authentication. Let me think about how to handle this.\n\nActually, looking at the context - the user is sharing a Feishu message that contains a password \"d8DUQdqH\". This password might be for the Apifox doc or it might be something else.\n\nWait, looking more carefully at the system message: it seems the user is quoting/replying to a previous message and the password is in that context. The message structure shows:\n- msg:om_x100b6fd3b8b980b0c3a462b9e222d78\n- reply_to:om_x100b6fd3e7b04880c2ee143f5c296f6\n\nAnd the actual content shared seems to just be \"d8DUQdqH\" which is likely the password.\n\nLet me try to fetch the document using web_fetch with the password. But web_fetch doesn't support authentication headers in a simple way. \n\nActually, I should ask the user - they seem to be sending me the password, so maybe I should try accessing the doc with it. But the way Apifox docs work, they're typically protected at the application level, not through HTTP auth.\n\nThe most practical approach is to ask the user to copy the actual document content since I can't access the Apifox doc with the password, or the user should share the content directly.\n\nWait - let me reconsider. The user's message shows they sent a password in the context. The document at Apifox needs a password. Maybe the password can be passed as a URL parameter or something?\n\n\nI'll need to ask the user to provide the document content directly since I can't authenticate with just a password through the available tools.","thinkingSignature":"0d4cb1cebc7604ede81b42c5b49b3d57e9154744af61d668b3d6a9a9d805f521"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n收到密码。不过 web_fetch 工具不支持带密码认证访问 Apifox 文档。\n\n你方便把文档内容直接复制粘贴给我吗？或者截图也行，我来帮你处理。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":565,"output":459,"cacheRead":47552,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":48576,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779335296476,"responseId":"065db380837ae4454361fb52bf550fa2"}}
