{"type":"message","id":"92da26f0","parentId":"fed6c601","timestamp":"2026-05-21T04:41:21.816Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user shared the documentation content directly - it's about 妙手开放平台 (Miaoshou Open Platform) API integration guide. This is the integration documentation for a platform that seems to be related to e-commerce/ordering (based on the order creation API example).\n\nKey information from the doc:\n1. **API Base URL**: `https://openapi-erp.91miaoshou.com`\n2. **Flow**: Register App → Get Keys → Generate Signature → Call API\n3. **Signature Algorithm**: HmacSHA256 with the formula:\n   `sign = HmacSHA256(appSecret, appSecret + path + timestamp + appKey + bodyJson + appSecret)`\n4. **Headers**: x-app-key, x-timestamp, x-sign\n\nThis looks like they want to integrate with this platform. I should ask what they want to do with it - what API calls they need to make, or if they want me to help build an integration.\n\nBut wait - there's also the earlier context about the OpenRouter API key test that failed with \"User not found\" error. The user was trying to test the DeepSeek model.\n\nLet me address both:\n1. First acknowledge the Miaoshou doc\n2. Note that the OpenRouter test failed - the API returned \"User not found\" error with a 401\n\nActually, looking at the conversation flow:\n- User asked about OpenRouter free models\n- User wanted to use deepseek/deepseek-v4-flash:free\n- I tried to test it and got a 401 error \"User not found\"\n- User then shared the Miaoshou doc\n\nSo these might be two separate topics. Or maybe the user wants to integrate with Miaoshou AND still fix the OpenRouter issue.\n\nActually, wait - the user just shared the doc directly as text in the message. So I can read it now. Let me acknowledge and ask what they need help with.\n\nFor the OpenRouter issue - the API key might be wrong or the account might have issues. The user shared two keys:\n1. sk-or-...75c4 (initially)\n\n\n2. sk-or-…75c4 (the full key that was actually in the config)\n\nThe test with curl failed saying \"User not found\" which suggests the API key is invalid or the account has issues.\n\nLet me address both topics - acknowledge the Miaoshou doc and note the OpenRouter issue.","thinkingSignature":"1c56f7076eae81a9cb620d6fdaf5d859ae048399cbfafe211c72fd2d36a00cd9"},{"type":"text","text":"文档读到了，这是**妙手开放平台**的对接指南，主要内容：\n\n**基本信息：**\n- API 域名：`https://openapi-erp.91miaoshou.com`\n- 认证方式：AppKey + AppSecret + 签名（HmacSHA256）\n- 签名公式：`appSecret + path + timestamp + appKey + bodyJson + appSecret`\n\n**你要接入妙手开放平台的什么功能？** 告诉我需求，我来帮你实现。\n\n---\n\n另外，OpenRouter 测试有问题 —— 刚才 curl 调用返回了 `{\"error\":{\"message\":\"User not found.\",\"code\":401}}`，说明 API Key 有问题或者账户有异常。\n\n你有两个 key：\n1. `sk-or-…75c4`（最初给的，疑似截断了）\n2. `sk-or-…75c4`（这个才是完整 key，已经写入配置）\n\n你确认一下 OpenRouter 账户是否正常？或者重新检查一下 API Key 是否正确。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":269,"output":769,"cacheRead":69423,"cacheWrite":5587,"totalTokens":76048,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779338465001,"responseId":"065dbfe1b1e4de7d8a0c0ffc45e30b85"}}
{"type":"message","id":"5e682073","parentId":"92da26f0","timestamp":"2026-05-21T04:41:25.677Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"user:ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b6fdc80011794b26fc8b75ad7518\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Thu 2026-05-21 12:41 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\"\n}\n```\n\n# 通过货源链接采集货源\n\n## OpenAPI Specification\n\n```yaml\nopenapi: 3.0.1\ninfo:\n title: ''\n description: ''\n version: 1.0.0\npaths:\n /open/v1/product/common_collect_box/common_collect_box/fetch_item:\n post:\n summary: 通过货源链接采集货源\n deprecated: false\n description: ''\n operationId: 6362ecb4b6c74dc5fde307cafc98050b\n tags:\n - 开放平台/商品/公共采集箱\n parameters: []\n requestBody:\n content:\n application/json:\n schema:\n type: object\n properties:\n collectLinks:\n type: array\n items:\n type: string\n description: 链接列表\n maxItems: 50\n required:\n - collectLinks\n x-apifox-orders:\n - collectLinks\n x-apifox-ignore-properties: []\n responses:\n '200':\n description: 成功\n content:\n application/json:\n schema:\n $ref: >-\n #/components/schemas/openJavaPartner_product_commonCollectBox_commonCollectBox_fetchItemResponse\n headers: {}\n x-apifox-name: 成功\n '500':\n description: error\n content:\n application/json:\n schema:\n $ref: '#/components/schemas/SimpleErrorResponse'\n headers: {}\n x-apifox-name: ''\n security: []\n x-apifox-folder: 开放平台/商品/公共采集箱\n x-apifox-status: released\n x-run-in-apifox: https://app.apifox.com/web/project/8149572/apis/api-446814581-run\ncomponents:\n schemas:\n openJavaPartner_product_commonCollectBox_commonCollectBox_fetchItemResponse:\n type: object\n properties:\n result:\n type: string\n code:\n type: string\n data:\n type: object\n properties:\n sourceItemIdAndDetailIdMap:\n type: object\n additionalProperties:\n type: integer\n description: 货源ID和公共采集箱ID的映射\n x-apifox-orders: []\n properties: {}\n x-apifox-ignore-properties: []\n x-apifox-orders:\n - sourceItemIdAndDetailIdMap\n x-apifox-ignore-properties: []\n x-apifox-orders:\n - result\n - code\n - data\n x-apifox-ignore-properties: []\n x-apifox-folder: ''\n SimpleErrorResponse:\n type: object\n properties:\n result:\n type: string\n description: 返回结果\n examples:\n - success\n code:\n type: string\n description: 结果码/错误码\n reason:\n type: string\n description: 错误信息\n examples:\n - 参数错误\n required:\n - result\n - code\n - reason\n x-apifox-orders:\n - result\n - code\n - reason\n x-apifox-ignore-properties: []\n x-apifox-folder: ''\n securitySchemes: {}\nservers: []\nsecurity: []"}],"timestamp":1779338485565}}
