{"type":"message","id":"5a04b6b8","parentId":"bcd787ca","timestamp":"2026-05-21T04:41:34.992Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is sharing the API documentation for the \"妙手开放平台\" (Miaoshou Open Platform) - specifically the \"通过货源链接采集货源\" (Collect products via source links) API.\n\nThis is an API endpoint:\n- Path: `/open/v1/product/common_collect_box/common_collect_box/fetch_item`\n- Method: POST\n- Description: 通过货源链接采集货源 (Collect products via source links)\n- Body parameters:\n  - `collectLinks`: array of strings (链接列表), max 50 items\n\nThis API is for collecting product information from source links (like from e-commerce platforms) and putting them into a \"common collection box\" (公共采集箱).\n\nThe user has already shared:\n1. The general integration guide (快速接入)\n2. This specific API documentation\n\nThey seem to want to integrate with this platform. I should ask what they need - do they have:\n1. AppKey and AppSecret for Miaoshou?\n2. What source links do they want to collect from?\n3. What do they want to do with the collected data?\n\nLet me acknowledge this API doc and ask what they need help with.","thinkingSignature":"3280a26ba483d3e07cded65cc6f32711dc52a50b9c0fadae2c24983495d72045"},{"type":"text","text":"这是**妙手开放平台的「通过货源链接采集货源」API**：\n\n**接口信息：**\n- **路径**: `POST /open/v1/product/common_collect_box/common_collect_box/fetch_item`\n- **功能**: 通过货源链接批量采集货源（最多50条链接）\n- **请求体**:\n```json\n{\n  \"collectLinks\": [\"链接1\", \"链接2\", ...]\n}\n```\n- **返回**: `sourceItemIdAndDetailIdMap` — 货源ID和公共采集箱ID的映射\n\n---\n\n**你需要什么帮助？**\n\n1. **已有 AppKey/AppSecret** — 给我，我帮你写调用代码\n2. **还没注册应用** — 告诉我你的需求，我帮你规划接入流程\n3. **想把这个功能集成到 Agent 工作流里** — 告诉我具体场景，我设计实现方案\n\n你现在是哪个阶段？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":269,"output":424,"cacheRead":69978,"cacheWrite":7101,"totalTokens":77772,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","times