{"type":"message","id":"791d9753","parentId":"953de6b2","timestamp":"2026-05-21T04:57:12.604Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good, I can reach the Miaoshou API. Now let me analyze what the user needs:\n\n1. They have a Feishu bitable (TTS发饰选品数据库 v2.0) with a button at the last row\n2. The button should configure an HTTP request that:\n   - Takes the \"1688同款链接\" field URL\n   - Submits it to Miaoshou ERP API: `/open/v1/product/common_collect_box/common_collect_box/fetch_item`\n   - Needs proper signature authentication\n\n3. They need help with:\n   - What to fill in the HTTP request configuration\n   - Solving the Miaoshou HTTP signature problem\n\nThe issue with Feishu's \"按钮\" (button) in bitable is that:\n1. Feishu buttons can be configured to make HTTP requests\n2. BUT the Miaoshou API requires a signature that is calculated using HmacSHA256 with the formula: `appSecret + path + timestamp + appKey + bodyJson + appSecret`\n3. This signature changes with every request (timestamp changes) and requires the appSecret which should NOT be exposed client-side\n\nSo the problem is:\n- Feishu buttons can make HTTP requests but can't compute the required HMAC signature client-side\n- The appSecret can't be stored in the button configuration (security risk)\n- The signature requires knowing the exact body content at request time\n\n**Solutions:**\n\n1. **Custom Webhook/Server approach**: Set up a middleware server that:\n   - Receives the Feishu button webhook\n   - Computes the signature using the appSecret stored server-side\n   - Forwards the request to Miaoshou with proper headers\n\n2. **Feishu Mini Program/Automation**: Use Feishu's automation to trigger a server-side function\n\n3. **No-code approach using Feishu Automation + OpenClaw**: \n   - Configure the Feishu button to trigger a webhook to OpenClaw\n   - OpenClaw agent receives the trigger, computes the signature, and calls Miaoshou API\n\nThe most practical no-code solution is option 3 - use OpenClaw as the middleware. OpenClaw has the tools to:\n- Receive webhook triggers\n- Compute the HMAC signature\n- Make the API call\n\nI'll explain this to the user and ask for their Miaoshou AppKey and AppSecret to proceed with setting up the integration.","thinkingSignature":"325fc00a13654e19fb8424cc88ccc150cfd954d8b4ab1994a429df972ddb1b11"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n好的，已经拿到飞书表格了。API 也能正常调通。\n\n**你的问题核心：**\n\n飞书多维表格的「按钮」支持配置 HTTP 请求，但妙手 API 需要 **HMAC 签名**，这个签名：\n- 每次请求都不一样（包含时间戳）\n- 需要 `appSecret` 才能生成\n- **不能放在前端按钮配置里**（暴露密钥不安全）\n\n所以飞书按钮**直接调妙手 API 行不通**，需要一个中转。\n\n---\n\n**解决方案：让 OpenClaw 作为中转**\n\n流程：`飞书按钮` → `触发 OpenClaw` → `OpenClaw 计算签名并调妙手 API` → `返回结果`\n\n你只需要告诉我：\n\n1. **妙手 AppKey**（格式：`ak_xxx`）\n2. **妙手 AppSecret**（格式：`as_xxx`）\n\n我来帮你配置好 OpenClaw 处理这个签名调用，你只需要在飞书按钮里填一个 Webhook URL 就行。\n\n先把这两个 Key 给我？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":197,"output":712,"cacheRead":78720,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":79629,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779339423231,"responseId":"065dc39fb9f992ffecb1ee5ab704b617"}}
{"type":"message","id":"eb5cecf8","parentId":"791d9753","timestamp":"2026-05-21T04:57:37.569Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"user:ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b6fdd4b1634a8c313bbf3101f50e\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Thu 2026-05-21 12:55 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\"\n}\n```\n\n[media attached: media://inbound/cd933bbb-6a86-4a96-9720-7e8e120908a0.jpg (image/jpeg) | media://inbound/cd933bbb-6a86-4a96-9720-7e8e120908a0.jpg]\n[Image]\nUser text:\n[Feishu ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb Thu 2026-05-21 12:57 GMT+8] ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb: /home/halei/.openclaw/media/inbound/cd933bbb-6a86-4a96-9720-7e8e120908a0.jpg\n这是我已经填写的内容，就是不知道那填写的不对\nDescription:\n这是一张自动化流程工具中“发送 HTTP 请求”的操作截图。\n\n**关键信息如下：**\n* **接口用途：** 调用的是 **妙手ERP (MiaoShou ERP)** 的 OpenAPI，用于“获取采集箱商品 (fetch_item)”。\n* **请求方法：** POST。\n* **请求地址：** `https://openapi-erp.91miaoshou.com/open/v1/product/common_collect_box/fetch_item`\n* **当前问题：** 你的请求体（Body）目前是空的 `{}`。\n\n**操作建议：**\n1. **查阅文档：** 该接口通常需要传递特定参数（如商品链接、平台类型等），请查阅妙手ERP官方API文档补充 Body 内容。\n2. **配置请求头（Headers）：** 开放接口通常需要配置 `Content-Type: application/json` 以及用于身份验证的 `AppKey` 或 `Token`。\n3. **测试：** 建议先用 Postman 或类似工具调试通后再填入此处的配置。"},{"type":"image","data":"","mimeType":"image/jpeg"},{"type":"image","data":"","mimeType":"image/jpeg"}],"timestamp":1779339457454}}
{"type":"custom_message","customType":"openclaw.runtime-context","content":"[media attached: media://inbound/cd933bbb-6a86-4a96-9720-7e8e120908a0.jpg (image/jpeg) | media://inbound/cd933bbb-6a86-4a96-9720-7e8e120908a0.jpg]\nTo send an image back, prefer the message tool (media/path/filePath). If you must inline, use MEDIA:https://example.com/image.jpg (spaces ok, quote if needed) or a safe relative path like MEDIA:./image.jpg. Absolute and ~ paths only work when they stay inside your allowed file-read boundary; host file:// URLs are blocked. Keep caption in the text body.\nSystem: [2026-05-21 12:57:14 GMT+8] Feishu[default] DM | ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb [msg:om_x100b6fdd4b1634a8c313bbf3101f50e, post, 1 attachment(s)]\n\n[Image]\nUser text:\n[Feishu ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb Thu 2026-05-21 12:57 GMT+8] ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb: /home/halei/.openclaw/media/inbound/cd933bbb-6a86-4a96-9720-7e8e120908a0.jpg\n这是我已经填写的内容，就是不知道那填写的不对\nDescription:\n这是一张自动化流程工具中“发送 HTTP 请求”的操作截图。\n\n**关键信息如下：**\n* **接口用途：** 调用的是 **妙手ERP (MiaoShou ERP)** 的 OpenAPI，用于“获取采集箱商品 (fetch_item)”。\n* **请求方法：** POST。\n* **请求地址：** `https://openapi-erp.91miaoshou.com/open/v1/product/common_collect_box/fetch_item`\n* **当前问题：** 你的请求体（Body）目前是空的 `{}`。\n\n**操作建议：**\n1. **查阅文档：** 该接口通常需要传递特定参数（如商品链接、平台类型等），请查阅妙手ERP官方API文档补充 Body 内容。\n2. **配置请求头（Headers）：** 开放接口通常需要配置 `Content-Type: application/json` 以及用于身份验证的 `AppKey` 或 `Token`。\n3. **测试：** 建议先用 Postman 或类似工具调试通后再填入此处的配置。","display":false,"details":{"source":"openclaw-runtime-context"},"id":"6f488cf5","parentId":"eb5cecf8","timestamp":"2026-05-21T04:57:37.645Z"}
{"type":"message","id":"524a1a3d","parentId":"6f488cf5","timestamp":"2026-05-21T04:57:44.236Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user sent an image showing their HTTP request configuration in the Feishu automation tool. Let me analyze it to understand what's already filled in and what's missing.\n\nLooking at the image description, the key information shows:\n- Request method: POST\n- Request address: `https://openapi-erp.91miaoshou.com/open/v1/product/common_collect_box/fetch_item`\n- Body is currently empty `{}`\n\nThe user configured it but it's not working. Looking at the actual path in the screenshot, it looks like `/open/v1/product/common_collect_box/fetch_item` (not the full path mentioned earlier which was `/open/v1/product/common_collect_box/common_collect_box/fetch_item`). Let me check if the path is correct.\n\nThe issues I can see:\n1. The path might be slightly wrong - based on the API doc, the correct path should be `/open/v1/product/common_collect_box/common_collect_box/fetch_item`\n2. Headers are missing - needs x-app-key, x-timestamp, x-sign\n3. Body is empty but should contain `{\"collectLinks\": [...]}`\n4. No Content-Type header\n\nThe user is using Feishu's automation to send HTTP requests, but the problem is:\n1. They can't compute the signature (needs appSecret which can't be stored in the automation)\n2. The body format might be wrong\n\nLet me read the image to see the actual configuration.","thinkingSignature":"388a738f08294c8e45dd3af98caa5add7bf4e4accac4fc139a8385ad24c54abb"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_mz2m44hj1n5x_1","name":"image","arguments":{"image":"/home/halei/.openclaw/media/inbound/cd933bbb-6a86-4a96-9720-7e8e120908a0.jpg","prompt":"Please describe in detail what you see in this screenshot, especially the HTTP request configuration fields: URL, Headers, Body, Authentication, etc. What values are filled in?"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7