{"type":"message","id":"84648ac2","parentId":"524a1a3d","timestamp":"2026-05-21T04:58:03.186Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_mz2m44hj1n5x_1","toolName":"image","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Based on the screenshot provided, here is a detailed description of the HTTP request configuration:\n\n**General Context:**\nThe image shows a configuration interface for an automation or integration tool, specifically for \"Step 2\" (第 2 步) which is set to \"Send HTTP Request\" (发送 HTTP 请求).\n\n**Configuration Fields and Their Values:**\n\n*   **Request Method (请求方法):** Set to **POST**.\n*   **Request URL (请求地址 (URL)):** The full URL filled in is:\n    `https://openapi-erp.91miaoshou.com/open/v1/product/common_collect_box/fetch_item`\n*   **Request Body:** Below the URL field is a code editor area for the request body. It currently contains an empty JSON object:\n    `{}`\n*   **Headers (请求头):** There is **no Headers section visible** in the current screenshot. It may be located further down the page or within a collapsed menu.\n*   **Authentication (身份验证):** Similarly, there is **no Authentication or Auth section visible** in this view. It might be under another tab or further down the scrollable area.\n\n**In Summary:**\nThe current configuration is set up to make a **POST** request to the specified **91miaoshou.com API endpoint** with an **empty JSON body**. Details regarding headers and authentication are not present in this specific image."}],"details":{"model":"minimax/MiniMax-VL-01","image":"/home/halei/.openclaw/media/inbound/cd933bbb-6a86-4a96-9720-7e8e120908a0.jpg","attempts":[]},"isError":false,"timestamp":1779339482969}}
{"type":"message","id":"e9afe0cd","parentId":"84648ac2","timestamp":"2026-05-21T04:58:10.186Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user has shared a screenshot of their HTTP request configuration. From the image analysis:\n\n1. **Request Method**: POST ✓\n2. **Request URL**: `https://openapi-erp.91miaoshou.com/open/v1/product/common_collect_box/fetch_item` ✓\n3. **Request Body**: Empty `{}` - this needs to be filled with `{\"collectLinks\": [\"...\"]}`\n4. **Headers**: Not visible in screenshot, but needs:\n   - `Content-Type: application/json`\n   - `x-app-key: ak_xxx`\n   - `x-timestamp: <unix timestamp>`\n   - `x-sign: <signature>`\n5. **Authentication**: Not visible\n\nThe main problems I can see:\n1. Body is empty - needs the actual content `{\"collectLinks\": [...]}`\n2. Headers are missing - x-app-key, x-timestamp, x-sign are required\n3. There's no signature being computed\n\nBut wait - looking at the API path they used: `/open/v1/product/common_collect_box/fetch_item` \nBut the correct API path according to the doc is: `/open/v1/product/common_collect_box/common_collect_box/fetch_item`\n\nThey might have the wrong path too.\n\nBut the fundamental issue is that even if they fill in all the correct values, they can't compute the signature in the button configuration because:\n1. The signature requires the appSecret\n2. The signature formula is: `HmacSHA256(appSecret, appSecret + path + timestamp + appKey + bodyJson + appSecret)`\n3. The timestamp changes every request\n4. The body might change based on the URL clicked\n\nSo my earlier assessment is correct - they need a middleware to compute the signature. The Feishu button automation cannot do this client-side.\n\nLet me explain this to the user and offer the OpenClaw middleware solution.","thinkingSignature":"b93fc0959babd365cdade1818bd2e9fcf7443213146a5047108b907620492a59"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n看到了你的配置，问题比较多：\n\n**问题清单：**\n\n| 字段 | 你的填写 | 问题 |\n|------|----------|------|\n| URL | `/open/v1/product/common_collect_box/fetch_item` | ❌ 路径不对，完整路径是 `/open/v1/product/common_collect_box/common_collect_box/fetch_item` |\n| Body | `{}` | ❌ 空，应该填 `{\"collectLinks\": [\"链接1\", \"链接2\"]}` |\n| Headers | 空白 | ❌ **缺少必需的头部**：x-app-key、x-timestamp、x-sign |\n| 签名 | 无 | ❌ **根本没填** — 这才是最核心的问题 |\n\n---\n\n**但最根本的问题是：**\n\n就算你把上面这些都填对了，你也**无法在飞书按钮里计算签名**，因为：\n\n1. 签名公式：`HmacSHA256(appSecret, appSecret + path + timestamp + appKey + bodyJson + appSecret)`\n2. 每次请求时间戳不同 → 签名每次都变\n3. `appSecret` 不能写在配置里（暴露了谁都能用你的账号）\n\n**所以飞书按钮直接调妙手 API 行不通，必须有个中转服务来计算签名。**\n\n---\n\n**我帮你做一个中转方案：**\n\n1. 你把妙手的 **AppKey** 和 **AppSecret** 给我\n2. 我在 OpenClaw 里写一个接收飞书按钮触发的接口\n3. OpenClaw 接收后自动计算签名、调妙手 API、返回结果\n4. 你在飞书按钮里只需要调用 OpenClaw 的 Webhook URL 就行\n\n这样做的好处：\n- AppSecret 只存在 OpenClaw 配置里，不会泄露\n- 签名自动计算，你不需要管\n- 飞书按钮配置简单到只需要填一个 URL\n\n**先给我妙手的 AppKey 和 AppSecret？**"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":413,"output":784,"cacheRead":80608,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":81805,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779339483194,"responseId":"065dc3dbc7d4425da871505bec165d7f"}}
{"type":"message","id":"d58755fd","parentId":"e9afe0cd","timestamp":"2026-05-21T06:50:02.299Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"user:ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b6fdeff953ca0c39f0cb07957070\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Thu 2026-05-21 14:49 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\"\n}\n```\n\n飞书不支持时间戳字段吗"}],"timestamp":1779346202188}}
